<view class="page">
  <view class="report-hero">
    <text class="eyebrow">赔偿测算</text>
    <view class="report-title">当前材料下的赔偿参考区间</view>
    <view class="amount">{{currentCase.estimateRange}}</view>
    <view class="warning-panel">
      金额为辅助测算参考，不保证最终赔偿结果。最终以协商、保险审核、调解或裁判结果为准。
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card confidence-card">
    <view>
      <view class="confidence-label">材料完整度</view>
      <view class="confidence-value">{{currentCase.progress}}%</view>
    </view>
    <view class="confidence-copy">
      还缺 {{currentCase.pendingCount}} 项关键材料。补齐后可重新测算。
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card item-list">
    <view class="list-title">赔偿项目</view>
    <view wx:for="{{claimItems}}" wx:key="name" class="claim-row">
      <view>
        <view class="claim-name">{{item.name}}</view>
        <view class="muted claim-detail">{{item.detail}}</view>
        <view class="basis">{{item.missingImpact}}</view>
      </view>
      <view class="claim-side">
        <text class="claim-amount">{{item.amount}}</text>
        <text class="muted evidence">{{item.evidence}}</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="card missing-card">
    <view class="section-title">影响测算的缺失项</view>
    <view wx:for="{{missingImpacts}}" wx:key="material" class="missing-row">
      <text class="missing-name">{{item.material}}</text>
      <text class="missing-impact">{{item.impact}}</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="action-stack">
    <button class="secondary-button" bindtap="goMaterials">补充材料后重算</button>
    <button class="primary-button" bindtap="checkout">生成处理材料</button>
  </view>
</view>
